Livestream is accepting applications for full time <strong>Live Production Hardware Support</strong> position available in our New York City office. <strong>The Live Production Hardware Support position assumes many varied responsibilities, which include but are not limited to the following</strong>:</p>
<p>
- Proactively monitor and test existing applications &amp; hardware configurations</p>
<p>
- Update and improve documentation for our hardware and software products </p>
<p>
- Work with the latest technologies</p>
<p>
- Works closely with the Producer Support team to troubleshoot and test customer issues</p>
